fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "gtkscale-h.html#gtk_scale_get_layout_offsets", "fragment": "Gtk.Scale.GetLayoutOffsets \nObtains the coordinates where the scale will draw the Pango.Layout representing the text in the scale. Remember when using the Pango.Layout function you need to convert to and from pixels using PANGO_PIXELS not introspectable or Pango.Constants.SCALE. \nIf the DrawValue property is false the return values are undefined. \nParameters \nlocation to store X offset of layout or null \nlocation to store Y offset of layout or null \nSince \n"});